Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:30.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}籠の中は安全で　绝对なのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:35.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造すら忘れた　その座に光は当たんないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}希望語る　不満散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}革命の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:43.20,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}誰にも追いつけないところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:50.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}突き抜け　修羅を越え　いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:55.71,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今にも圧倒的な支配が　僕の喉を乾かしたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:03:00.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奪わせないものは夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:03.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}燃やせ　全神経の感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:07.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}誰に届けたいかすらもわからない音に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:13.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}意義は宿らない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:18.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}その頂へと
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:30.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}牢笼里多么的安全　舒适而没有压力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:35.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}忘却了创造　这里将被光明抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来倾吐希望　让不满爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}吹响革新的号角
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:43.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我要全力攀登　再不让他人企及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:50.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}突破血雨腥风　让他们全都辟易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:55.71,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}绝对的控制　将令我咽喉干渴无法言语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:03:00.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}却无法夺去我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:03.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}让一切感官嘶吼激昂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:07.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不把炽热的情感寄托在音符中唱响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:13.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}怎会令心脏热血滚烫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:18.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我需要光　更多的光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}向着顶点冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I'm proud of myself and you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.70,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We must be the change we wish to see
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:57.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}青天響く霹靂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:23:01.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}閃光眩むその間に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:08.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}決して音を立てずに　じっと忍び寄る影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:11.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}騙し騙されて 失った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:15.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}罵り罵られて 奪った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:19.31,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}守りべき正義をすり減らして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:22.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}勝ち取るものなどない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:26.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}籠の中から見上げた空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:29.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}雨上がりの青の眩しさに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:33.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}囚われたままじゃ居られない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:36.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}昔話なら捨てて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:40.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}従うべきは他でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.72,0:23:44.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}突き動かすほどの本能だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:47.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}ぼくはぼくじゃなきゃ居られない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:50.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}変われるほど器用じゃないさ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:57.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}响彻青天的霹雳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:23:01.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}闪光掠过的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:08.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}无声无息　阴影迫近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:11.83,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}尔虞我诈　逐渐失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:15.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}以眼还眼　互相争夺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:19.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}逐渐磨损本该保护的正以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:22.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}也绝对不会赢得任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:26.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}在笼中仰望到的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:29.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}雨过天晴眩目的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:33.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}不甘永远被囚禁于此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:36.83,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}哪怕要让我舍弃过去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:40.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}要遵从之物仅有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.72,0:23:44.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}本能激发着无穷动力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:47.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}无论如何都要做自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:50.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}因为改变对我是难题
